attachments.title: Uncorked’s Take on Design Week PDX + What We’re Doing
attachments.text: It’s that time of year again… The week where designers and creatives, as well as other curious folks from different disciplines, swarm various areas of the city to be a part of Design Week Portland. While the overarching theme of this multi-day event may be obvious, there are many ways to participate, including attending presentations, workshops, events, exhibits, mixers and more. Beyond that, the areas of thought that are being represented are across the board—from architecture and music to manufacturing and graphic design.
